# Your business content lives on OneDrive, NOT GitHub.
# Only the reusable scaffold (CLAUDE.md, README, templates, empty index) is
# committed. Everything ingested from OneDrive stays out of git.
#
# Exception: `xfreight-*.md` files are distilled documentation seeds (synthesized
# from CLAUDE.md / docs/knowledge-base/ which are already public in this repo),
# not raw business data. They live in git so the GitHub Actions librarian
# (karpathy_compile.yml) can compile them into /wiki on its cron runs.
_build/
raw/*
!raw/README.md
!raw/xfreight-*.md
